Makefile was altered to have the following rules:

all
    Will compile all plugins in one single shared object following the LADSPA API.

LV2all
    Will compile all plugins in one single shared object following the LV2 API.

LV2single
    Will compile all plugins in each analog shared object following the LV2 API.

PLUGINNAME_
    Will compile only this plugin following the LV2API.

installLV2 (will work only after at least one of the 3 rules above)
    Will install all shared objects and ttls in the directory DEST.

installLADSPA
    Will install all shared objects and rdfs in the directory DEST.
